This paper is primarily focused on deep neural networks and their regularization techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also evaluates the effectiveness of Sparseout on image classification (cs.CV) and language modelling (cs.CL), which are common applications of deep learning. Additionally, the paper proposes a new regularization technique, which could be considered a contribution to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
